    This class serves as instance of Gitlab component Branch. To create or delete this branch, call create() or delete() explicitly. This doesn't support update. This supports query for branches within GitlabProject. See GitlabBranch.ProjectQuery. Gitlab Web API: https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/api/branches.html
